%h2 FAQs

%h4 Will the eBooks work on my eReader?

%p
	After purchase, we send you a link to download in files for Kindle, Nook, iPad, and any reader that takes the ePub format. We also include links on how to get your new eBook onto Kindle, Nook and iPad. If you have another reader that takes ePub, just consult the manufacturer's site to see how to add the file.
%h4 Glad to hear the files will work, but how do I get them onto my eReader?
%p
	Every eReader is a bit different, so it's hard to give a one-size-fits-all answer to this question.  We recommend consulting your specific eReader's documentation.  Here are some resources for the most common readers:
	
