%h4 Can I order more than one thing? Where's my shopping cart?

%p
	Absolutely! You can order however many different items you like, but the "continue shopping" option is still pending.  Instead, if you don't see the combo you want, you'll have to place multiple orders for now.  We're working on adding the shopping cart functionality.


